      <title>GROW Investment 称中国人民银行担心人民币面临压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-20/pboc-concerned-about-yuan-pressure-grow-investment-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[GROW 投资集团合伙人兼首席经济学家洪灏告诉彭博电视台，对于中国人民银行而言，“货币稳定是比利率更重要的政策目标”。周三，中国人民银行行长潘功胜在上海发表讲话时暗示了利率改革以及可能在二级市场交易国债。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-20/pboc-concerned-about-yuan-pressure-grow-investment-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 02:15:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
